# Changelog

## [3.0.0] – 2024-07-17
### Added
- **Fully automatic installation** – Ubuntu, XFCE4, Termux:X11 install automatically when needed
- **Modular architecture** – Clean separation of concerns
- **One-command installer** – Downloads all components from GitHub
- **Auto-update** – Checks for updates every 24 hours
- **Backup Manager** – Backup/restore .bashrc

### Changed
- Complete rewrite from monolithic to modular
- All dependencies auto-installed
- Better error handling and logging

